Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀大夫 究竟发生什么事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让末将也知道一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我们与吕布交战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}京都长安发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊天动地的剧变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董卓部旧将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李傕 郭汜劫掠天子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来又反目为仇 大砍大杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子和百官被沦为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被郭李二人是拉来拉去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整个长安是一片废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}血流成河 断水断粮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子以粗糠腐肉为食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百官更是奄奄待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}捡要紧的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要紧的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子在安集将军董承的相助下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}侥幸逃脱了长安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星夜向东逃往洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子在逃亡途中写下此诏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急召天下诸侯前去勤王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此良机 千古难觅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}良机 主公 这叫什么良机呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从长安到洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须经过芒砀山一带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此山离兖州不足五百里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公想起兵救驾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待天子到手之后 就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可以挟天子以令诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}掌天下之柄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子已经逃出长安了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急诏各镇诸侯前去护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们说说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是奉诏还是不奉诏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 依许攸之见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公非但应该奉诏赶去护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且还必须抢先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为当今天下纷乱动荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诸侯争雄 但只是各霸一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这种时候谁若能把天子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}握于掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁就可以执天下牛耳已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸之言 真乃匹夫之见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现如今天下大势一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那昔日天子不过是徒有虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汉室摇摇欲坠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公若要真把他请来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那无异于是给自己添了个累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}试问 天子如果来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这冀州谁是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是主公你还是那个小娃儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果他摆起皇帝谱来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天一诏明日一旨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听是不听 从是不从啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰说得有理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天子也确实是个累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不救也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方才田丰所言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那才真正是鼠目寸光 愚夫短见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大汉虽然是摇摇欲坠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可尚未崩溃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天子虽然年少无为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且徒有虚名 可他仍为汉帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你虽贵为冀州之主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可你仍是汉帝之臣哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有道是 名不正则言不顺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}言不顺则必败也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 天子可不是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是一面号召天下诸侯的皇旗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一面统领三军的大纛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其作用可限量乎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公弃而不取
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定会落入别人掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁会去取
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州的曹操 荆州的刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们都会去取
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是那曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但会取 甚至会去抢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸之言危言耸听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么大旗大纛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那昔日天子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过是寒秋中的一片落叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无用之物罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操想要 任由他取去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公应该不尚虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}专心实际
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问当今最大的实际是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我以为 是迅速消灭公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兼并青州 幽州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果此役成功 那天下神州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公已独占四州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这和真正的天子又有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以主公应该整军备战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迅速兼并青 幽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}切勿分心旁鹜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我意已决 不奉天子诏令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}集中精力 整军备战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等秋收过后 粮饷备足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻发兵进取幽州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公短见啊 庸臣误国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一只小小的传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各路诸侯尚且争来抢去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可一个活生生的皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却怎么没人要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主是庸主 臣是佞臣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痛快 痛快 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们跟太阳一块登上芒砀山了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经一天一夜走了五百多里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这人不累 马也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们还是歇息歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行 那就稍歇片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等日上三竿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}继续出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍有什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冀州的探报回哨说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍没有奉旨前来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍离芒砀山如此的近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是他却没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人昏庸到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是叫人喜欢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术和刘表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南阳的袁术没有行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州的探哨回报也没有到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}估计他们也不可能前来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来 天子非我莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的意思是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来救驾的非我不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山下的驿道发现车辙印儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}轮间尺幅有多宽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}轮间尺幅六尺六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}六尺六 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子的坐驾已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上出发 全力追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 从车辙上看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这车已经驾过去很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们要是追不上怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是给我追到洛阳城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}追到长乐宫 追到上天入地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要把天子给我追到手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这 五百多里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们还是歇一会儿再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才你已经下令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说太阳到了三竿咱们再出发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经三竿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可在我这儿看还不到两竿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说三竿就三竿 你说没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下 陛下 慢点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总算是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下回宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 小心一点儿 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 我们总算是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下 陛下 来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总算是回宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先坐一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一路的奔波 总算是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕渴 朕饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 整座皇城都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有水 连护城河都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 祖宗保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最艰难的时候都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下这次咱们重返东都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定能振兴大汉哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜皇上回朝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李傕和郭汜追来了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下放心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}李郭二贼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早被我们甩到八百里以外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 不好了皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好了 不好了皇上 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}启禀皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城东出现了大批的兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快要进关了皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿 爱卿 怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完了 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上天无路 入地无门哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祖宗哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睁开眼看看皇朝的子孙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}护佑大汉社稷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办 怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们快点拿主意呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大喜呀 大喜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救兵 救兵来了 皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下 祖宗显灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救兵到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是谁来救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是冀州的袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉诏前来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他离洛阳最近哪 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 忠臣哪 忠臣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救兵不 不是冀州袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是兖 兖州刺史 曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么是曹操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真没想到曹操能来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍离洛阳最近却坐视不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而曹操却从千里之外赶来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 这真是家贫见孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}患难见忠臣哪 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊皇上 是啊皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待会儿曹操来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可要好好地奖赏他几句呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊皇上 可要好好的奖赏他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕知道 朕重重地夸奖他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 给朕更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 给皇上更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有个事儿忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依礼 外臣觐见天子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都得上供点什么 我走的匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么都没准备 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 在下倒有个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子和百官肯定是饥寒交迫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们现在最需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一口肉汤 两只面饼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一口肉汤胜似万两黄金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 当年我亡命的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馋肉汤馋得真是要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}熬汤去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一事 请主公在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公拜见天子时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必恪守朝廷礼法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让天子和百官们安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一件事你也得考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}洛阳已成废墟不能再用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们接驾之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该在何处建都为妥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州府许县
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为那是主公的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公把天子放在自个儿的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才会安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实主公早就想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但不愿直言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么把我的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}琢磨得这么透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 这是做属下的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣 兖州刺史曹操 叩见吾皇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠臣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}患难见忠臣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿平身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吾皇万岁 万岁 万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿 这是何物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请陛下一猜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玉玺 玛瑙 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕猜不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请陛下揭盖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 这是刚刚烹熟的鸡汤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕已经半年多没有识过肉味了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请陛下用膳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位大人 请用膳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 有吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}终于有吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别抢 别抢 大家都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣 恭请陛下校阅兖州将士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿啊 这些将士都是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 他们都是天子的将士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有多少兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}精兵五十万 战将上千员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}了不起 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你比董卓他们 英雄十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这 有曹将军在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃朝廷之幸 大汉之福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乱贼可灭 大事可期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在应该奖赏曹操才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕拜你为大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授武平侯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今天起你就是这天下的栋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣谢吾皇厚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜武平侯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下 臣有本进奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}东都洛阳眼下已是残破不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宫廷庙宇皆为乱军所废
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且 洛阳距西凉贼军太近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣为天子安危所计
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为中兴大汉宗室所想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请迁都许昌 重建朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重振朝纲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事万万不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}洛阳虽然残破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却是二百年帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天灵地秀 虎踞龙蟠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是曹操的老巢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果迁都于许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那不是掉进曹操的囊中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}言之有理呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下看看吧 陛下好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有在许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才能得到这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}精兵猛将的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷才能安然无忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕准奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迁都于许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿 朕刚刚逃出狼窝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却又落入虎穴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可怎生是好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事已至此 陛下应该韬光养晦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.91,0:24:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}观时待变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.55,0:24:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操会不会把朕杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自已当皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.22,0:24:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操只是想把陛下握于掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为他所用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用 为他所用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.50,0:24:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那朕岂不成了个器物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.11,0:25:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:25:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.65,0:25:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.15,0:25:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上以汉帝之名拟旨诏告天下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.95,0:25:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说天子将帝都迁于许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.22,0:25:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏告各州诸侯 太守
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.39,0:25:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刺史 将军速速前来朝拜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.90,0:26:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外 自即日起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌更名为许都
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.80,0:26:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷改年号为建安并大赦天下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇上有旨 宣百官入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.90,0:26:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇上有旨 宣百官入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.20,0:27:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吾皇万岁万岁万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.51,0:27:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平身
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.11,0:27:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.95,0:27:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下 自从迁都许昌以来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.86,0:27:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下军民无不欢欣鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.49,0:27:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交口称幸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}九州也是海晏河清 雨顺风调
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 这都是爱卿之功
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.50,0:27:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕 欢喜得很
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.01,0:27:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请陛下恩旨
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.24,0:27:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加封冀州袁绍为大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.35,0:27:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授武亭侯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.05,0:27:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加封南阳袁术为骠骑将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.75,0:28:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授忠义侯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.35,0:28:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加封荆州刘表为前将军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.56,0:28:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授东安侯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.06,0:28:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加封幽州公孙瓒为后将军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授靖安侯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.60,0:28:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 天子刚刚移驾许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.21,0:28:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百废待兴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.01,0:28:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何要急于嘉奖各路诸侯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是因为刚刚迁都
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.55,0:28:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才要恩威天下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.55,0:28:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}机不可失 时不我待
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.75,0:28:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足下在这道奏章里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.16,0:28:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把袁绍 刘表 公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.73,0:28:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这各路诸侯都封赏了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.80,0:28:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有的还升授两三级
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.30,0:28:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可独独没有你自个儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.91,0:28:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想当年
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.91,0:28:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董卓还把自己封个什么相国
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.95,0:29:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚至还自号尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.65,0:29:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为何不请旨加恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.05,0:29:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那正是董卓的狂妄和愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.66,0:29:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是董卓 我是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.60,0:29:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣世受国恩 知恩图报
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.40,0:29:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只想为陛下尽忠不想贪图虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.14,0:29:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明白了 足下是务实不务虚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凡曹爱卿所奏 朕无不照准
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.20,0:29:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.81,0:30:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷颁发诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}封我为大将军 加授武亭侯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.35,0:30:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷还把冀州 青州
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.65,0:30:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚至我们一直
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.66,0:30:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}图谋攻取但还没有到手的并州
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.46,0:30:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也一并的敕封给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.53,0:30:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们说说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.40,0:30:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此诏我是接还是不接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.75,0:30:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜主公荣领大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.35,0:30:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此诏当接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.05,0:30:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷刚刚迁于许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:30:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子自顾无暇
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此诏只不过是一道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.76,0:30:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺水人情罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.93,0:30:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 依在下之见
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.23,0:31:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这道诏书表面上看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.44,0:31:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是个顺水人情
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.70,0:31:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实际上是暗藏祸心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.71,0:31:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.45,0:31:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这道诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.65,0:31:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是以皇帝的名义下诏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.85,0:31:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可从那诏书的字里行间中
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.85,0:31:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不难看出那每一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.16,0:31:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是曹操的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.16,0:31:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你一旦接下此诏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.96,0:31:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就须上表谢恩 如此一来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.33,0:31:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就等于主公你承认了那曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.43,0:31:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挟天子以令诸侯是合法的了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.94,0:31:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公如果不接此诏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.11,0:31:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又有违臣道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.91,0:31:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操会说你身为汉臣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却对杭朝廷 此外
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.05,0:31:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是一恩诏 主公便接了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.65,0:31:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天再来一恶诏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.55,0:31:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令主公或纳粮 或退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.56,0:32:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚至是让你割地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.23,0:32:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那时主公你是接还是不接
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.13,0:32:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此 此诏接与不接均属两难
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.41,0:32:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是那曹贼的祸心已然得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.55,0:32:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉 我后悔没有采纳先生之言
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.65,0:32:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早把天子夺到手里那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.26,0:32:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挟天子令诸侯的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.43,0:32:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不是他曹操 而是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.43,0:32:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我兵马将士比他多二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.74,0:32:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城池属地更比他多两倍有余
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.24,0:32:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我甚至可以把朝廷安在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.15,0:32:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皆因我一时疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.35,0:32:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让曹操占了先机
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.75,0:33:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反过来倒要听他的矫诏 乱命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.06,0:33:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惜啊 当初我的这个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.93,0:33:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却被那鼠目寸光之人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.23,0:33:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说成是 匹夫之言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.84,0:33:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事皆因我迟疑而耽误
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.64,0:33:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与列位公卿无关
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.85,0:33:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说我们现在该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.95,0:33:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 臣下可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.46,0:33:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五年之内 你与那曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.83,0:33:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必将有一场生死之战
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟有这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.54,0:33:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你不妨想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.54,0:33:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操为何要挟天子以令诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.45,0:34:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又为何遍封了各地诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而独独不封他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.05,0:34:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为在他眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.35,0:34:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他已然是天子 天子就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.16,0:34:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他已经执天下牛耳
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.46,0:34:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用不着再自封了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.83,0:34:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 现在的曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.43,0:34:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}论属地之广不及你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.03,0:34:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}论兵马之强
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.04,0:34:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}钱粮之多也不如你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.44,0:34:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可那曹操他一定会充分利用
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.44,0:34:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挟天子以令诸侯之利
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一步步 逐渐地壮大起来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.85,0:34:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 曹操可远非董卓可比
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.45,0:34:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他比董卓要阴险狡诈百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.96,0:34:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人志在天下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.53,0:34:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到 当年和我一块儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃喝镖赌的臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.24,0:34:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天却要和我争夺天下了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.04,0:35:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.98,0:35:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操非但要跟你争天下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.75,0:35:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鹿死谁手 犹未可知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我绝不会坐视曹操为患
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.03,0:35:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我绝不会坐等曹操有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.83,0:35:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向我挑战 我再和他一决雌雄
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.13,0:35:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}众卿听令 秋收过后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.84,0:35:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即发兵十五万攻取幽 并二州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.44,0:35:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后 厉兵秣马 剿灭曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.54,0:35:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.68,0:35:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 倘能如此
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.08,0:35:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公幸甚 天下幸甚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.04,0:36:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.64,0:36:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍 袁术 刘表 公孙瓒等
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.04,0:36:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都接受了朝廷的敕封
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.08,0:36:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上表谢恩了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.28,0:36:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.55,0:36:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向朝廷谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.36,0:36:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是向我曹操谢恩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.53,0:36:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.33,0:36:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说袁绍他们此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.43,0:36:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心中当是何等滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.94,0:36:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又苦又酸 又忌又恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.48,0:36:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}养一个天子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.58,0:36:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比自个儿做天子舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.68,0:36:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公当心啊 此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.39,0:36:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可是各路诸侯心目中的大敌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.46,0:37:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚有一天我跟他们必有一战
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.23,0:37:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是眼下他们还顾不上我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.03,0:37:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍正忙着和公孙瓒交战
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.93,0:37:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想攻取幽州
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.24,0:37:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术正图谋独霸江南
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.14,0:37:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.84,0:37:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们也应该抓紧时机进取中原啦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.58,0:37:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公心里头一直还惦记着徐州吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.59,0:37:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何止是惦记
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.89,0:37:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}简直是朝思暮想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.26,0:37:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲成大业 必取徐州啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州一日不得 我一日不安
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.83,0:37:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是眼下刘备和吕布盘踞在徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们二人相互支援 着实棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.88,0:37:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.68,0:37:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急攻 则二人同心相拒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.29,0:38:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宽忍 则必生分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.76,0:38:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经宽忍许久了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.23,0:38:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何以不见他们分裂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.23,0:38:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公要取徐州 在下倒有一计
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.24,0:38:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.74,0:38:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公可以天子的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.54,0:38:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给刘备下一道诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.48,0:38:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}册封他为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.48,0:38:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除徐州各郡之外
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.08,0:38:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还可以把袁术的南阳郡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.78,0:38:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一并敕封给他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.49,0:38:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同时下道密令叫他出兵征讨袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.39,0:38:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说袁术图谋不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.83,0:38:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暗怀称帝之心
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.23,0:38:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备乃汉帝后裔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.73,0:38:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对朝廷是忠心耿耿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.63,0:38:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚做了徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.74,0:38:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他岂敢不尽忠效命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.94,0:38:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与此同时我再以天子之名
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.04,0:38:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给袁术下一道诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说刘备心怀叵测
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给朝廷上表密奏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.99,0:39:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说他袁术有称帝之心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.09,0:39:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要发兵攻袭他的首府南阳郡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.49,0:39:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.39,0:39:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.83,0:39:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样一来 刘备和袁术之间
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.13,0:39:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必有一场恶斗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.73,0:39:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是你死就是我活
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.54,0:39:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后他们会同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.24,0:39:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我们 就可以伺机攻取徐州了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公圣明
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.48,0:39:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驱虎吞狼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子诏书到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.99,0:39:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏偏将军刘备接旨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.19,0:39:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备接旨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.43,0:39:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺天承运 皇帝诏曰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.03,0:39:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备自提领徐州以来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.94,0:40:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠心护国 保境安民 朕心甚慰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.24,0:40:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今特命其为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}领徐州六郡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.98,0:40:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并封车骑将军 武义侯 钦此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.69,0:40:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刘备领旨谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.86,0:40:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜将军晋升为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.73,0:40:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外 陛下还有一道密诏给将军
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.94,0:40:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}盼将军务必遵行
